tests
=====

Directory for utility programs for tests.


listPLOptions.cxx
-----------------

Program to print the available base physics lists and EM options
which can be then used in test_physics_lists.sh.

To run the program:
  ./listOptions [-b base lists ] [-em em options ] [-v verbose]
      -b    list available base physics lists
      -em   list available EM options
      -v    precede lists with a title
